   <title>
    <narrative xml:lang="EN">Expected Results</narrative>
    <narrative xml:lang="FR">R&#xE9;sultats escompt&#xE9;s</narrative>
   </title>
   <indicator measure="5">
    <title>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">Results expected</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="FR">R&#xE9;sultats escompt&#xE9;s</narrative>
    </title>
    <description>
     <narrative xml:lang="FR">Les r&#xE9;sultats attendus de ce projet comprennent : (1) l&apos;engagement accru des soci&#xE9;t&#xE9;s de droit d&apos;Afrique de l&apos;Est de plaider en faveur d&apos;une r&#xE9;forme du droit afin de refl&#xE9;ter les principes de transparence, de sensibilit&#xE9; au genre et d&apos;imputabilit&#xE9; des industries extractives; (2) la participation accrue de la communaut&#xE9;, en particulier des femmes, pour faire progresser leurs droits li&#xE9;s aux industries extractives.</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">The expected outcomes for this project include: (1) increased engagement of East African law societies to advocate for law reform to reflect the principles of transparency, gender sensitivity and accountability in the extractive industries; and (2) increased community participation, particularly women, to advance their rights related to the extractive industries.</narrative>
    </description>
